  "contents": "<div class=\"content markitup-box\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t我家里有一份中国地图出版社出版的中国地图册，里头竟然把台湾纳入中国领土：<br/>\n<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly9pLmltZ3VyLmNvbS9LVE1TakZTLmpwZw\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://i.imgur.com/KTMSjFS.jpg\"><img alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/KTMSjFS.jpg\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/KTMSjFS.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><br/>\n还有更恐怖的，竟然把台湾的主要城市描绘得非常详细：<br/>\n<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly9pLmltZ3VyLmNvbS9JWEVwOHhzLmpwZw\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://i.imgur.com/IXEp8xs.jpg\"><img alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/IXEp8xs.jpg\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/IXEp8xs.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><br/>\n<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly9pLmltZ3VyLmNvbS9udmgxZU5RLmpwZw\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://i.imgur.com/nvh1eNQ.jpg\"><img alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/nvh1eNQ.jpg\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/nvh1eNQ.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><br/>\n<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly9pLmltZ3VyLmNvbS9nSGRIYWFTLmpwZw\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://i.imgur.com/gHdHaaS.jpg\"><img alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/gHdHaaS.jpg\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/gHdHaaS.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><br/>\n<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly9pLmltZ3VyLmNvbS9tUHZiS1A5LmpwZw\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://i.imgur.com/mPvbKP9.jpg\"><img alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/mPvbKP9.jpg\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/mPvbKP9.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><br/>\n<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly9pLmltZ3VyLmNvbS9mSGVHZEthLmpwZw\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://i.imgur.com/fHeGdKa.jpg\"><img alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/fHeGdKa.jpg\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/fHeGdKa.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly9pLmltZ3VyLmNvbS9lWWFIV1FVLmpwZw\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://i.imgur.com/eYaHWQU.jpg\"><img alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/eYaHWQU.jpg\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/eYaHWQU.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><br/>\n还有，在油管上看有关南岛语系的视频的时候，竟然还有人管台湾叫台湾省。<br/>\n真是太恐怖了。\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>",
